Uses of Package
com.google.appinventor.components.scripts

  • Packages that use com.google.appinventor.components.scripts 
    Package Description
    com.google.appinventor.components.scripts
    Provides classes for generating information about components from the annotations and comments in their source code.
  • Classes in com.google.appinventor.components.scripts used by com.google.appinventor.components.scripts 
    Class and Description
    ComponentProcessor
    Processor for generating output files based on the annotations and javadoc in the component source code.
    ComponentProcessor.ComponentInfo
    Represents an App Inventor component, including its designer properties, Simple properties, methods, and events.
    ComponentProcessor.Event
    Represents an App Inventor event (annotated with SimpleEvent).
    ComponentProcessor.Feature
    Represents a component feature that has a name and a description.
    ComponentProcessor.Method
    Represents an App Inventor component method (annotated with SimpleFunction).
    ComponentProcessor.Parameter
    Represents a parameter consisting of a name and a type.
    ComponentProcessor.ParameterizedFeature
    Represents a component feature that has a name, description, and parameters.
    ComponentProcessor.Property
    Represents an App Inventor component property (annotated with SimpleProperty).
